{"arkId":"cl010114984","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010114984","modified ":"2025-10-31","title":"Cafeti\u00e8re aux armes de la famille Mecklembourg","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Cafeti\u00e8re aux armes de la famille Mecklembourg"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Monarchie de Juillet (1830-1848) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque contemporaine)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1838 - 1845","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 562 - Marie d\u0027Orl\u00e9ans, Acc\u00e8s r\u00e9serv\u00e9","room":"Salle 562, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1838,"endYear":1845,"imprecision":"","text":"2e quart du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Lebrun, Marc-Augustin","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1782","place":"M\u00e9zi\u00e8res ?","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1859","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 12286","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"orf\u00e8vrerie, argenterie ; cafeti\u00e8re","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"La cafeti\u00e8re, de forme tr\u00e8s pansue, offre une profusion d\u2019ornements, cisel\u00e9s avec une grande virtuosit\u00e9. Les pieds sont form\u00e9s de cuirs enroul\u00e9s, d\u2019o\u00f9 s\u2019\u00e9chappent des l\u00e9zards, encadrant des t\u00eates de sanglier \u00e0 larges oreilles. La panse, tr\u00e8s renfl\u00e9e, est orn\u00e9e de rinceaux entrelac\u00e9s se d\u00e9tachant en relief sur un fond mat poin\u00e7onn\u00e9. Au-dessus, une petite frise de masques n\u00e9o-Renaissance, alternativement masculins et f\u00e9minins, marque la base de l\u2019encolure. L\u2019anse, \u00e0 d\u00e9cor de cuirs d\u00e9coup\u00e9s, se termine par une t\u00eate d\u2019animal. Un dragon, dress\u00e9 sur ses pattes arri\u00e8re, se retourne avec un \u00e9tonnant mouvement de torsion, pour  former le bec verseur ; il semble en m\u00eame temps veiller sur le petit dragon juch\u00e9 sur le couvercle.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; Fabricant (M.L., une girouette, un aigle) (au revers)\r ; France, argent, depuis 1838, titre et garantie (sur le col)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Profondeur","value":"15,5","displayDimension":"15,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"24,5","displayDimension":"24,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"25,5","displayDimension":"25,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Famille Desaint, Li\u00e8ge ; galerie Bernard de Leye, Bruxelles ; acquisition, 2009","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"achat","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"08\/10\/2009","startYear":2009,"endYear":2009},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9\/d\u00e9cision","value":"13\/10\/2009","startYear":2009,"endYear":2009}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"achat"}],"period